  <name>MCPI-Reborn Extended</name>
  <summary>Community-made MCPI-Reborn mod.</summary>
  
  <metadata_license>MIT</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      A community-made mode for MCPI-Reborn by MCPI Revival, which itself is a mod of Minecraft: Pi Edition by Mojang. The mod adds tons of cool new features, like:
    </p>
    <p>
      - Working sounds - Sprinting via the [CTRL] key - 1.18 textures - Custom skins - Sneaking via both the Shift and Alt keys - A custom &quot;Cursed Chest&quot; block - Ability to look around via arrow keys instead of mouse (useful if mouse is glitched) - Coloured terminal output
    </p>
    <p>
      and soooo much more! For more info, check out the github repository or drop by our support server: https://discord.gg/XJJNG9jTuh.
    </p>
  </description>
  
  <url type="homepage">https://github.com/mobilegmYT/mcpi-reborn-extended/</url>

